Question: Each image contains a wolf, and one image shows a black wolf and a dark doberman in a face-to-face confrontation.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/56/32/6c/56326c57e1798f1ad0139480a8013aa0.jpg

Right image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/cZuNEWbUbuE/maxresdefault.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many wolves are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many wolves are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a black wolf and a dark doberman in a face-to-face confrontation?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a black wolf and a dark doberman in a face-to-face confrontation?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 1 and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} and {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
